column2: "This is Amduscia, 10 years ago...there doesn't seem to be any differences worth mentioning. The atmospheric composition is roughly the same."
"How do you feel? No discomfort, dizziness? ...Excellent."
"It seems that regardless of how far back in time you travel, you can only remain a short while. Let's finish what we need to--"
"...and already it seems this isn't going to be easy. Remember, you can't call for help in this timeline. Stay alert!!"
"Friendly fire!? Who would be so reckless!?"
"Huh? I thought you said there were only Darkers in this vicinity?"
"...oh, i see. A humanoid form. You must be a Dark Falz, right?"
"...Error. Parameters do not match observed values. Claris Claes, this individual is not a Darker."
"...eh? EEH!? B-but you said...so I...!!"
"I made no such statement. I spoke only of such a possibility."
"Geez! You...ngh!"
"A-aha-haha...um..."
"I'm very sorry! It was a mistake!"
"1. It's no problem, Claris Claes."
"2. Are you Claris Claes?"
"...Huh? W-why do you know my name?"
"I don't speak to other ARKS, let alone meet any at all..."
"...wait, are you able to hear her voice?"
"Seriously!? An order comes right when I'm in the middle of a conversation!!"
"Please forgive me! I won't make the same mistake, I promise!"
"...<%me>. I think you already know, but it's her."
"The second Claris Claes from 10 years ago... is none other than Matoi."
"She looks exactly the same as she does in the present? Hm, I don't have any data. All the records are missing, after all."
"But there was this report, as if to cover it all over:"
"'Claris Claes the Second halted the Darker invasion at the expense of her life."
"...the fact that we met her here proves our thinking was right. Let's continue investigating the truth of 10 years ago."
